msg.data:
Graph Modification

Please visit the relevant section in pgql-lang.org for more details.

paragraphs.title: Inserting vertices (1)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT VERTEX x LABELS ( Male ) PROPERTIES ( x.age = 22 )
""");

%pgx
graph2.queryPgql("""
SELECT ID(x), LABEL(x), x.age
  FROM MATCH (x)
""")

paragraphs.title: Inserting edges
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
  INSERT EDGE e BETWEEN x AND y
  FROM MATCH (x)
     , MATCH (y)
  WHERE id(x) = 1 AND id(y) = 2
""");

paragraphs.title: Labels
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT EDGE e BETWEEN x AND y LABELS ( knows )
  FROM MATCH (x:Person)
     , MATCH (y:Person)
 WHERE id(x) = 1 AND id(y) = 2
""");

paragraphs.title: Properties (vertex)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT VERTEX v PROPERTIES ( v.age = 22 )
""");

paragraphs.title: Properties (edge)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT EDGE e BETWEEN x AND y LABELS ( knows ) PROPERTIES ( e.since = DATE '2017-09-21' )
  FROM MATCH (x:Person)
     , MATCH (y:Person)
 WHERE id(x) = 1 AND id(y) = 2
""");

paragraphs.title: Multiple inserts in the same INSERT clause (vertex)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT
  VERTEX v LABELS ( Male ) PROPERTIES ( v.age = 23, v.name = 'John' ),
  VERTEX u LABELS ( Female ) PROPERTIES ( u.age = 24, v.name = 'Jane' )
""");

paragraphs.title: Multiple inserts in the same INSERT clause (vertex and edge)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT VERTEX x LABELS ( Person ) PROPERTIES ( x.name = 'John' )
     , EDGE e BETWEEN x AND y LABELS ( knows ) PROPERTIES ( e.since = DATE '2017-09-21' )
  FROM MATCH (y)
 WHERE y.name = 'Jane'
""");

paragraphs.title: Multiple inserts in the same INSERT clause (edge)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
INSERT EDGE e BETWEEN x AND y
  FROM MATCH (x)
     , MATCH (y) -> (z)
 WHERE id(x) == 1
""");

paragraphs.title: Update (vertices)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
UPDATE x SET ( x.age = 42 )
  FROM MATCH (x:Person)
 WHERE x.name = 'John'
""");

paragraphs.title: Update (multiple vertices and edges)
paragraphs.text:
%pgx
graph2 = graph.cloneAndExecutePgql("""
UPDATE v SET ( v.carOwner = true )
     , u SET ( u.weight = 3500 )
     , e SET ( e.since = DATE '2010-01-03' )
  FROM MATCH (v:Person) <-[e:belongs_to]- (u:Car)
 WHERE v.name = 'John'
""");
